# REST Client file Profile

### Update user profile
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/identity/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "isActive": true,
  "email": "john.smith@example.com"
}

### Delete user profile
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/identity/profile
Accept: application/json

### Logical delete user profile
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/identity/profile/logical-delete
Accept: application/json
